<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Booking Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h3 {
            background-color: #0073e6;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        strong {
            color: #0073e6;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #ff6600;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h3>New Booking Request</h3>
        <p>
            A new booking has been requested by <strong><%= email %></strong> for a stay from 
            <span class="highlight"><%= localtimeFrom %></span> to <span class="highlight"><%= localtimeTo %></span>. 
            The reservation includes <strong><%= adult %></strong> adults and 
            <strong><%= children %></strong> children, requiring <strong><%= room %></strong> room(s).
            You can contact the customer via email at <strong><%= email %></strong> or by phone at 
            <strong><%= phno %></strong>.
        </p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing us! We will contact you shortly to confirm the booking.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
